name: Transferred to 2.7.4.24
classes: Phosphotransferases with an alcohol group as acceptor
comment: Transferred entry: diphosphoinositol-pentakisphosphate kinase. Now EC 2.7.4.24, diphosphoinositol-pentakisphosphate kinase. The enzyme had been incorrectly classified as the reaction involves transfer of a phospho group to another phospho group (EC 2.7.4) rather than to an hydroxy group (EC 2.7.1)
